"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-record-breaking-wildschutt-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport  ByWesley Botton  Chief sports journalist  2 minute read  27 January 2024  09:06 am  Adriaan Wildschutt in action during the men's 10 000m final at last year's World Athletics Championships in Budapest.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriaan_Gilles_Camper\", \"score\": 0.9847498192067099, \"rank\": 0.015486350436425645, \"text\": \"Adriaan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriaan_Gilles_Camper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriaan_Gilles_Camper\"}, {\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9992969046081388, \"rank\": 0.00035991032430437883, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 204, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungaroring\", \"score\": 0.5505233269902102, \"rank\": 0.8164534476287187, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungaroring\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungaroring\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Anton Geyser/Gallo Images  Distance runner Adriaan Wildschutt says he has his sights firmly set on this year's Olympic Games after opening his season in explosive fashion on Friday night.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.023467799398986e-14, \"text\": \"Geyser\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\", \"score\": 0.8885636023131664, \"rank\": 0.12517441581710365, \"text\": \"Gallo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriaan_Gilles_Camper\", \"score\": 0.9847498192067099, \"rank\": 0.015486350436425645, \"text\": \"Adriaan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriaan_Gilles_Camper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriaan_Gilles_Camper\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing at a meeting held at Boston University, Wildschutt charged to an impressive victory in 12:56.76, shattering his own South African 5 000m short track (indoor) record.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University_Terriers\", \"score\": 0.46239257066174844, \"rank\": 0.7601837504130681, \"text\": \"Boston University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University_Terriers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University_Terriers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"12:56.76 from Adrian Wildschutt\\u2026.AND a collegiate record from Nico Young!Wildschutt of@NAZ_Elitekicks past Young in the final lap to post the fastest men's 5k of the day at the John Thomas Terrier Classic.Young clocked a NCAA 5k record of 12:57.14 \\ud83d\\udc40#BUTerrierClassicpic.twitter.com/VVZoafXz7V  The 25-year-old athlete made history by becoming the first SA athlete to dip under 13 minutes over the 5 000m distance on any surface.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Thomas_(Christadelphian)\", \"score\": 0.47734787296015624, \"rank\": 0.4209849105158408, \"text\": \"John Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Thomas_(Christadelphian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Thomas_(Christadelphian)\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9042169258840282, \"rank\": 0.10592917656922497, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9997268380760411, \"rank\": 0.00014691008768832154, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the process, he shattered his own national short track mark of 13:09.30 which he set in Boston in February last year.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.999178190050093, \"rank\": 0.0005909582408788439, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wildschutt, who had already qualified for the 5 000m event at the Olympics, felt his latest result was a big step forward towards the Paris Games in August.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My big focus is the Olympics, so everything in-between is just getting ready for that,\\\" he said in an interview withFloTrack.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not going to be racing a lot, so each race when I come in I will try to be as ready as possible and get fast times.\\\"\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9994383647824151, \"rank\": 0.000559220039700762, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Download our app  Get the latest news and updates on Whatsapp  The latest news directly in your inbox  Support Local Journalism  2026 The Citizen.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Whatsapp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights R